Title: Plea by govt. pleader in molestation case closed
Content: The Kerala High Court on Wednesday closed a petition filed by Dhanesh Mathew Manjooran, a government pleader at the High Court, seeking to quash a molestation case registered against him.Justice Sunil
Author: Special Correspondent
